             were indicted for <rs id="t18210411-20-off116" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18210411-20-off116" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18210411-20-off116" type="offenceSubcategory" value="housebreaking"></interp>
               burglariously breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18210411-20-victim305" type="victimName">
                           Ephraim 
                           Harris
                        <interp inst="t18210411-20-victim305" type="surname" value="Harris"></interp>
